&lt;li&gt;Engage cross-functionally across mechanical, firmware, and manufacturing teams to drive process improvements and efficiencies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Quickly prototype new products for proof of concept study.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with JDM partners to build and execute robust test plans and complete full programs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
