&lt;li&gt;Some experience with board level circuit design and prototyping.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to travel up to 15%.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good verbal and written communication skills, able to work independently and cross functionally.&lt;/li&gt;
